{"tid":2401990,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"日媒曝Apple與台積電合作開發超先進顯示器　在桃園龍潭秘密進行","createTime":"2021-02-10T06:43:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T08:38:45.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"834cfcc4f81a268ab99a6f90d418c16bb6e45c97","tid":2401990,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T06:43:01.000Z","msg":"據《日經亞洲評論》（NIKKEI Asia）引述未具名知情人士報導，美國蘋果公司（Apple Inc.）已與台積電（2330）合作，在Apple位於台灣的一處秘密設施開發Micro-OLED顯示器技術。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，這種微型OLED的面板尺寸不到1吋。據知情人士透露，這項超先進顯示器計劃在位於桃園龍潭區的Apple秘密實驗室中進行，目前處於試產階段，需要數年時間才能實現量產，部分生產也將用到台積電現有的晶片生產設備與製程。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士也說，Apple已從台灣面板業者友達（2409）聘用數十名經驗豐富的專家來推進micro OLED計劃，同時也從日本及其他地方挖角面板專家。這些人都必須簽署嚴格的保密協議，禁止與同業的朋友或熟人見面。<br />\n<br />\n這項計劃是Apple在龍潭秘密實驗室進行的2項計劃之一。除了micro OLED面板外，Apple也在開發micro LED技術，2項計劃都設試產線。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210210/5JAFA3OK45D5VLHBEMJ7PJMXVU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210210%2F5JAFA3OK45D5VLHBEMJ7PJMXVU%2F&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQtMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=b0e526d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210210%2F5JAFA3OK45D5VLHBEMJ7PJMXVU%2F&h=124df94d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210210/5JAFA3OK45D5VLHBEMJ7PJMXVU/</a>"},{"pid":"6b4e1a9f0d4537f402e08629b388e1ee7d4449e2","tid":2401990,"uid":178579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T06:45:33.000Z","msg":"盤前TSM🤫"},{"pid":"7cfcdffc073f2ea967fddfddc3c5743513dd97d1","tid":2401990,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T06:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52536930a27dd99fe170b75b58b017713ddf24a1","tid":2401990,"uid":333199,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T06:56:13.000Z","msg":"有春用<br />\n<br />\n台積弱有利好消息都唔會識升<i